The file `/up-cebu-exchange/up-cebu-exchange/public/fonts/poppins/Poppins-Regular.ttf` is a font file and cannot be generated as text content. You need to download the Poppins Regular font file from a font provider (like Google Fonts) and place it in the specified directory.

To download and integrate the Poppins Regular font, follow these steps:

1. Go to [Google Fonts](https://fonts.google.com/).
2. Search for "Poppins".
3. Select the "Regular 400" style.
4. Download the font files.
5. Extract the downloaded files and locate `Poppins-Regular.ttf`.
6. Move `Poppins-Regular.ttf` to the directory `up-cebu-exchange/up-cebu-exchange/public/fonts/poppins/`.

After placing the font file in the correct directory, you can proceed with the configuration and usage as described in the previous instructions.